QuestData.Title: Pests
QuestData.Description: Confound it all! These rat-faced thieves keep getting into all of our supplies! I swear, anything that's not tied down, and even some things that are, they nip off with'.$b$bYou want to make a difference for the war effort in Zandalar? Pop off as many of those buggers as you can find. $b$bOtherwise, get on with it!
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay $1oa Thieving Snappers in the Alliance Docks.
